{"tid":98194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連陶傑都將農曆新年同中國捆綁","createTime":"2017-01-28T08:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T12:11:13.000Z","uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51b8ccaf6368212f2f67148fe20f8c91f45f69a5","tid":98194,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"尋晚《光明頂》19話後生仔好憎中國，但話取消農曆新年又唔制。但星加坡人夠好憎中國，佢地都慶祝農曆新年。19都而家仲唔明農曆新年係成個東亞人文習俗，唔再關中國事。有為中國叫乜春節。"},{"pid":"fa854a1dd0562576c086b460710a14ba08b3dd03","tid":98194,"uid":16827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a262b18a4725fd6f01188139d4039e46baece2","tid":98194,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"唔係喎<br />\n我聽到佢話唔好將強國文化同強國捆綁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa496134f6bdab0aba22b33af561c1acbdd5794","tid":98194,"uid":39320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"重聽啦你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528e4144f2d6f44912d94bcf99af2de39ba8d6ca","tid":98194,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係喎<br />\n我聽到佢話唔好將強國文化同強國捆綁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話民國嗰隻係好，唔係另一樣野。佢係唔俾其他國家慶祝農曆新年，大中華膠係事實。"},{"pid":"a3399661a4aed955655066c12318ae154391bb97","tid":98194,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係喎<br />\n我聽到佢話唔好將強國文化同強國捆綁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話民國嗰隻係好，唔係另一樣野。佢係唔俾其他國家慶祝農曆新年，大中華膠係事實。</blockquote><br />\n民國係另一回事，可能會令人哋接受多啲中國文化，依家我講嗰個問題係農曆新年唔係只係中國嘅嘢。民國違風正唔正同我嘅話題無關。"},{"pid":"0f3e3c1d259e21b008a73d2d91b2595d56b4aca3","tid":98194,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"慶祝舊歷新年唔係支那人既專利<br />\n日本人慶新年一樣都會比利是"},{"pid":"b2a29c9c16ae34a586a43d7717969baa36fa35b3","tid":98194,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"支那狗玩老屈最叻"},{"pid":"247c7b61c617ce6e39477f4f9def398d8845a674","tid":98194,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"似你將隻耳同個腦捆綁"},{"pid":"24da568f3c0746be8ee1baf49b0d373c042aa4b8","tid":98194,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慶祝舊歷新年唔係支那人既專利<br />\n日本人慶新年一樣都會比利是</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本用新曆，舊曆連假都唔會放"},{"pid":"c4e24a0b499005c1e395a0e7fd9cf86a519f6da2","tid":98194,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那狗玩老屈最叻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人知道有鬼用"},{"pid":"043e62dc23950f91986f9be01d9ac5bd7e4c6582","tid":98194,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"陶傑話屎食得你唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc8ed0136c24a93bba71fceb49f7533b2a4f57d","tid":98194,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8d028948bd82f685f8191f76fc96615f9185b36d","tid":98194,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係喎<br />\n我聽到佢話唔好將強國文化同強國捆綁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話民國嗰隻係好，唔係另一樣野。佢係唔俾其他國家慶祝農曆新年，大中華膠係事實。</blockquote><br />\n陶傑係民國膠黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e06d4696afc5d3522022817298003f141b8d9d5","tid":98194,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係喎<br />\n我聽到佢話唔好將強國文化同強國捆綁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話民國嗰隻係好，唔係另一樣野。佢係唔俾其他國家慶祝農曆新年，大中華膠係事實。</blockquote><br />\n陶傑係民國膠黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但民國已經名存實亡，不過呢個都係題外話。我意思係19太霸道，將農曆新年當係只屬於中國嘅節日。上面講左東亞同東南亞好多國家都放假同慶祝，好似筷子同紙張，唔通用呢啲嘢就係中國人？<br />\n香港建國成功使唔使廢除農曆新年？"},{"pid":"cae7cb5b33671a36ddee297d4793b1f016131ab5","tid":98194,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>慶祝舊歷新年唔係支那人既專利<br />\n日本人慶新年一樣都會比利是</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本用新曆，舊曆連假都唔會放</blockquote><br />\n我意思係 慶祝舊歷新年唔代表係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}